# Project Template: Complete Setup Guide

This document contains **everything** you need to recreate the project infrastructure. It includes the full content of all configuration and boilerplate files.

## 1. Project Structure

Create the following directory structure:

```
.
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/
│   │   ├── login/
│   │   └── signup/
│   ├── globals.css
│   └── layout.tsx
├── lib/
│   └── prisma.ts
├── prisma/
│   └── schema.prisma
├── public/
├── .env
├── auth.config.ts
├── auth.ts
├── middleware.ts
├── next.config.ts
├── package.json
└── tsconfig.json
```

---

